    "description": "Volkswagen India Logistics Global Group, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Distribution Manager for our Nagpur operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Volkswagen India Logistics Global Group:\nVolkswagen India Logistics Global Group is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n• Ensure proper handling, packaging, and labeling of goods\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Reverse Logistics\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n• Proficiency in KPI Monitoring\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in Cold Chain Logistics\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Learning & development budget\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Nagpur, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Volkswagen India Logistics Global Group!",
